import { configureStore } from '@reduxjs/toolkit'
import loading from './reducer/loading'
import user from './reducer/user'
import account from './reducer/account'
import khoaThi from './reducer/khoaThi'
import donViDangKyDuThi from './reducer/donViDangKyDuThi'
import heDaoTao from './reducer/heDaoTao'
import hinhThucDaoTao from './reducer/hinhThucDaoTao'
import hoiDong from './reducer/hoiDong'
import monThi from './reducer/monThi'
import truong from './reducer/truong'
import nam from './reducer/nam'
import notify from './reducer/notify'

const store = configureStore({
  reducer: {
    loading,
    user,
    account,
    khoaThi,
    donViDangKyDuThi,
    heDaoTao,
    hinhThucDaoTao,
    hoiDong,
    monThi,
    truong,
    nam,
    notify,
  },
})
export default store
